      • MeterHyperVirial

        public MeterHyperVirial()

      • MeterHyperVirial

        public MeterHyperVirial(ISpace space,
                        boolean doFull)
        If full is true, then the pressure is also calculated and three values are returned. The first is the hypervirial value that would be returned normally. The second is the pressure. The last is hypervirial/(dim*dim*n) + pressure/density This is part of the expression for dP/drho
        Parameters:
        space -
        doFull -
